${goto 15}${color2}Mode+m 			${goto 130}${color1}Rofi  costum menu

${goto 15}${color2}Mode+<>			${goto 130}${color1}Change focus left right up down
${goto 15}${color2}Mod+Shift+<>		${goto 130}${color1}Move focused window  left right up down
${goto 15}${color2}Mode+h			${goto 130}${color1}Split horizontal
${goto 15}${color2}Mode+v			${goto 130}${color1}Split vertical
${goto 15}${color2}Mode+f			${goto 130}${color1}Toggle fullscreen 

${goto 15}${color2}Mode+s			${goto 130}${color1}Change container layout stacking
${goto 15}${color2}Mode+w			${goto 130}${color1}Change container layouttabbed
